GET YOUR FLU VACCINATION NOW
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Residents are encouraged to defend themselves against getting the
    flu by having a flu jab now.

    The best time to have a flu vaccine is in the autumn, from the
    beginning of October to the end of November. Whilst anyone can get
    vaccinated throughout winter, it is important to get protected
    before the cold weather settles in.

