HELP COMMEMORATE HOLOCAUST MEMORIAL DAY
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Residents, community groups, businesses and schools are invited
    to take part in this Richmond Council Holocaust Memorial Day
    (HMD) project.

    HMD 2020 is particularly poignant as it is the 75th anniversary
    of the liberation of Auschwitz-Birkenau and this will be a moving
    tribute to the millions who died.

